show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/SqfWHN
show.description:
By day, he’s a humble cleaner. By night, he’s Ghost—the ruthless syndicate head feared across the underworld.
When he saves a wealthy woman from a predator, his hidden world collides with his personal life, even as he conceals the truth from his own son.
Now, every step forward is a battle against enemies, betrayal, and the impossible balance between fatherhood and vengeance.
